  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Using a Melee Weapon or Unarmed Strike you can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and<strong> 1 SP</strong> to attempt to send an enemy hurling through the air.</p><p>Make an <strong>Attack Check </strong>against the <strong>PD </strong>of a target within 1 Space of you, and it makes a <strong>Physical Save</strong>.</p><p><strong>Attack Hit: </strong>It takes your Weapons damage.</p><p><strong>Save Failure: </strong>It gets knockback horizontally up to 3 Spaces + 1 additional Space for every 5 they fail the Save by.</p><ul><li><strong>Airborne:</strong> You can choose to knock the enemy vertically into the air. When you do, they move half the total distance and may be subjected to fall damage.</li><li><strong>Knock Prone:</strong> After the result, you can choose to reduce the total distance the target is pushed by 1 Space to knock them <strong>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.7470a07f7581c21e.JournalEntryPage.78d57fafb2f0d47e]{Prone}</strong> instead.</li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Technique Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><ul><li><strong>Extended Knockback:</strong> <strong>(1 SP)</strong> Increase the Knockback distance by 2 Spaces and increase the damage by 1.</li><li><strong>Painful Knockback:</strong> <strong>(1 SP)</strong> Increase the damage by 2.</li><li><strong>Bash & Smash:</strong> <strong>(1 SP, 1 AP)</strong> Change the Target from one creature to every creature within 1 Space.</li></ul>",
